CreateDatabaseUser is a BusinessTask
    owned by security
    stored in environment

    Parameters
        Service
        DatabaseLoginName is Alpha size 100
        Password          is Password

    Parameter Rules
        Service           required
        DatabaseLoginName required

    Actions

        CreateDatabaseUser is an Instance Action

            Action Rules

                invoke Create Identity
                    invoked.Service     = Service
                    invoked.Identity    = com.lawson.apps.security.base.Identity_ActionBase.generateDatabaseIdentityKey(DatabaseLoginName)
                    invoked.ServiceType = "Database"

                    invoked.DatabaseIdentityProperties.DatabaseLoginName = DatabaseLoginName
                    invoked.DatabaseIdentityProperties.Password          = Password
